1
00:00:02,280 --> 00:00:05,110
Rarity: Oh, Opalescence,
can't you just picture it?

2
00:00:05,160 --> 00:00:08,080
Moi stepping out
in a stunning new gown

3
00:00:08,120 --> 00:00:11,040
at the Grand Galloping Gala
in Canterlot.

4
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:12,910
[ Whoosh! ]

5
00:00:12,950 --> 00:00:15,000
Meow!

6
00:00:15,040 --> 00:00:17,580
Why, yes, I did make it myself.

7
00:00:17,630 --> 00:00:19,800
Thank you so much
for asking.

8
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:21,300
[ Tink! Tink! Tink! ]

9
00:00:21,300 --> 00:00:25,010
[ Purring ]

10
00:00:25,050 --> 00:00:26,260
[ Growls softly ]

11
00:00:26,300 --> 00:00:28,010
Oh, oh, well, of course
you can help me.

12
00:00:28,050 --> 00:00:29,100
Thank you.

13
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,430
Meow!

14
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:35,980
What's that?
You want to help me more?

15
00:00:35,980 --> 00:00:39,060
Oh, aren't you
the sweetest thing?

16
00:00:39,110 --> 00:00:42,320
Meow!

17
00:00:42,320 --> 00:00:43,940
Careful now.
Don't move.

18
00:00:43,990 --> 00:00:46,110
This shouldn't take long
at all.

